Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.85,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第七回  「信奈上洛」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥戴将军上洛的计划泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军虽然被暗杀了  但是还有弟弟义昭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把义昭奉为新的将军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就有上洛的大义名分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁被暗杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是将军足利义辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义辉公没有被暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是弟弟  是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏的事件应该是将军被暗杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军在千钧一发之际逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹义昭大人一起逃往大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史要是走向我不知道的岔路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在价值就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子要从树上掉下来咯  猴子前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来代替连猴子的智慧都没有了的相良前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表一个好提案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被织田家抓住的今川义元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有足利家的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有继承将军家的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今川义元奉为下一任将军上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  不枉我让你加入织田家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上相良前辈并超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么织田军开始上洛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中有浅井和六角等强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真够缠人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田和浅井应该结盟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想和浅井为敌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啊  为敌又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怕的是你那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟到处宣扬要结婚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里被取消婚事的话就成天下人的笑柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  你要是哭着求我  也许可以考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这事就当没发生过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能结婚的话  我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当帮帮我  请一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的妹妹嫁给你好了  感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有听说过信奈大人有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有啦  说有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再啰嗦就取消婚事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪求您妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  信长也有个妹妹的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝世美女  阿市！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  姐姐大人…这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始你就是浅井长政的夫人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是欺诈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被发现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可糊弄不了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了打下美浓就给我美少女作为奖励的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给我的话  我就不干活咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我美少女啦  美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我这么无聊的事情  你真不要脸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人拼命的理由  只有那个吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会遵守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚洗干净给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢  是谁呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我的胸部…那么好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐撒娇  给100分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前辈  请对我温柔点哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个都很赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里果然应该是要高岭之花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义元妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本就对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么我要给猴子糟蹋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要满怀感激地  接受奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是天下第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心  心理准备还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人说要奖励你  猴子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女  宁宁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始就来当猴子大人的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺诈啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅井长政结盟的信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始向南近江进军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了六角承祯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近了京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这个阵容  京都就近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来看看京都里的美女  结果完全变成荒凉之地了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就入室抢劫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三好军的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他们吗  怎么看都像山贼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为幕府倒台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都已经成了无法之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈让我们来打探是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是想确认今天的日本中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了统治者的国家的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和五右卫门先去收集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生你们请去姬巫女大人所在的大和御所看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人是站在大和的顶点的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是创建这个国家的诸神的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人崇拜供奉着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我所在的世界  似乎有微妙的不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子有一种不可思议的气质呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢去袭击御所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会轻易放过你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关白  近卫前久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗中操纵公家和政治的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鼠辈已经被砍头…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下贱者的人头谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你们还是三好三人众  这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堺之豪商  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了钱什么都肯做的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打倒了将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生这种事  连一文都没赚到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨敌退散  南蛮覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统领比叡山的正觉院豪盛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把南蛮人当作仇敌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从南蛮人手里保护这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须由我们来掌权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们必须要有姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  近卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你肯出面了啊  弹正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永弹正久秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不在乎地反复倒戈和谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战国的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说姬巫女大人是重要的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箕作城也攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到对所有的城池进行同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角一定惊呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里有很多优秀的武将嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有空跟他一点点耗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可以说是妙策  95分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前辈  现在一定为立不了功而不爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  京都那边比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来似乎很混乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半兵卫和五右卫门也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  解决掉六角去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法想象这里就是京都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界不是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我  卑贱之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们尝尝必杀奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸亦当如此强力剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  西洋修女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发和巨乳的组合  破坏力太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦是不能通过暴力治愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈祷吧  给予你的敌人爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来好好地爱一下你的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  我还是第一次骑大洋马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为日本之民  要知道羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:14:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  我梵天丸也不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找～到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葡萄牙来的传教士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝·弗洛伊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相良良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破坏的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默示录里的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们真不走运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来京都传教的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时我都在堺的南蛮寺里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来朝廷请求在全国传教的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他们说西洋人不能靠近御所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想见见姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想同样是侍奉神的姬巫女大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终结战乱之世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让国家变得安居乐业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那也是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想只要不放弃就会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会让人感觉很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是对此深信不疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有观音寺城了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气攻下它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是劝他们来投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为他们会答应的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意投降的话  就放他们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必去追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是让他们逃跑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是符合公主殿下的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事根本是闻所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们能成功上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要做出无谓的流血牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角那个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是战至最后一人  拖住织田信奈就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角大人会不会逃到甲贺的深山里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么凄惨也该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统治着越前的朝仓义景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被称作名门的大大名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让傻瓜公主上洛  这世道也算走到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里将今川义元那样的乡下大名辅佐为将军  才是原本的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要得到那位公主  并添加到余的作品中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣还真是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是哪里的笨蛋让足利将军的妹妹逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想愚弄我们吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是有意见的话  就把越前七十五万石的朝仓当作对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内讧可没有任何好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三好和朝仓  再加上武田和上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能形成信奈包围网了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完成这个是需要花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈上洛的速度应该更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且先撤兵  在京都周围燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈花时间灭火的话  余的士兵和武田、上杉家就能赶过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就交给你们了  三好三人众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要由我们来迎击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有松永弹正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军要拼死与信奈战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余也会伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对信奈恨之入骨的男人  也来助一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是京都最糟糕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想亲眼看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论百姓如何悲叹痛苦  不出来看一看是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂且不说未来  这个地狱是现在真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  她知道我是来自未来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百姓们能够欢声笑语的世界会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何能够断言？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有织田信奈在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈夺取天下之后  会创造一个崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都欢笑着  和弗洛伊斯姐姐一样的西洋人做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能和平生活的世界  信奈一定能创造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是信奈的梦想吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈的梦想也是大家的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  只要不放弃的话  梦想终会成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头有点晕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永弹正  前来迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来带我回去的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当作是你被无礼之徒强行带着到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准对他们动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老老实实跟你回去  这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了  相良氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五右卫门  半兵卫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气息…是被鬼魂什么的袭击了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的送到这里就行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不可思议的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在这里的巫女吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴  这次玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕由衷地表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…巫女殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  织田信奈终于完成了上洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都成为织田家所统治的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你说的  我让京都的治安恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像相当严重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这样应该就会好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了应该做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的地方还有很多很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我夺取天下之前罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个和平的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:35.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:40.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:46.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:06.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:23.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:34.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:43.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:47.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:35.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷时代纷争的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:40.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无奈伫立  独自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:46.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在寻觅着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}坚韧的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住内心幽然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:06.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能聆听到救赎之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有寻觅着的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}经历风花雪月的洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:23.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再犹豫  愿与你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:34.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之梦的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:43.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请记住  属于你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:47.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此处
